title: ATP World Tour 250, Marseille Men's Singles Results
text: February 20, 2018 / 9:56 PM / Updated 42 minutes ago UPDATE 3-ATP World Tour 250, Marseille Men's Singles Results Reuters Staff 1 Min Read Feb 21 (OPTA) - Results from the ATP World Tour 250, Marseille Men's Singles matches on Tuesday .. 1st Round .. 9-Karen Khachanov (RUS) beat Ruben Bemelmans (BEL) 6-3 7-6(2) Stefano Travaglia (ITA) beat Hugo Gaston (FRA) 6-2 6-2 8-Filip Krajinovic (SRB) beat Joao Sousa (POR) 3-6 6-4 6-4 Gilles Simon (FRA) beat Maximilian Marterer (GER) 7-6(3) 7-6(4) Pierre-Hugues Herbert beat Norbert Gombos (SVK) 6-2 7-6(3) (FRA) Ilya Ivashka (BLR) beat Laslo Djere (SRB) 6-3 6-1
